name: Deep Six V3 / Voyager Combo
details:
Deep Six V3 and Voyager Preamp/Overdrive/Compressor in one pedal Channel strip in a stompbox with transparent-sounding overdrive and studio-grade compressor
Simple 3-knob layout makes dialing in your dirt a breeze on Voyager
Level, Sustain, Attack, Tone, and Blend compressor controls on Deep Six V3
Adds clarity to your notes at lower-gain settings and gives edge to your solos at higher-gain settings
Shapes your tone at low compression settings and adds sustain at high settings
D+V, D/V switch enables you to use the effects individually, exclusively, or in combination
True-bypass switching preserves your tone when the effect is switched off
Runs internally at 18 volts for maximum headroom
Onboard polarity-correction circuit
Robust, attractive die-cast enclosure
